        <headline>Heat Advisory issued July 5 at 6:33AM CDT until July 5 at 8:00PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>* WHAT...Heat index values up to 105 expected.

* WHERE...Palo Duro Canyon State Park.

* WHEN...From 11 AM this morning to 8 PM CDT this evening.

* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures and high humidity may cause heat
illnesses.
</description>
        <instruction>Take extra precautions when outside. Wear lightweight and loose
fitting clothing. Try to limit strenuous activities to early morning
or evening. Take action when you see symptoms of heat exhaustion and
heat stroke.</instruction>
